    {
      "id": "PopularPost46964",
      "post_content": "Before there was [Blaze](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blaze), there were the original sister X-burners - [Fireball](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fireball) and Disintegrate. Both are strictly better than Blaze, and both were printed at the common rarity. Disintegrate was particularly effective against pesky regenerators like [Drudge Skeletons](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Drudge Skeletons), but was more often used as a game-ender, dealing damage directly to your opponent. A classic combo of the time used [Channel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Channel) and either Disintegrate or Fireball to turn a small lead into an instant win.",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost46964\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Before there was <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Blaze\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blaze\">Blaze</a>, there were the original sister X-burners - <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fireball\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fireball\">Fireball</a> and Disintegrate.  Both are strictly better than Blaze, and both were printed at the common rarity.  Disintegrate was particularly effective against pesky regenerators like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Drudge Skeletons\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Drudge Skeletons\">Drudge Skeletons</a>, but was more often used as a game-ender, dealing damage directly to your opponent.  A classic combo of the time used <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Channel\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Channel\">Channel</a> and either Disintegrate or Fireball to turn a small lead into an instant win.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '46964'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (1/19/2010 10:36:58 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n    